    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>halved</strong> <strong>green beans </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Wash your <strong>shredded kale</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
