    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the beans have started to soften, add the <strong>shredded kale</strong> to the pan with your<strong> ginger paste </strong>and<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Add a small splash of <strong>water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 3-4 min further or until the greens are tender with a slight bite</p>",
