      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>sriracha </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan</p><p>Squeeze in the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<strong> lime[s]</strong> and add a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, then give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>spicy stir-fried greens</strong></p>",
